"63:4:18" : {s: 63, a: 4, w: 18, r: "حذر", t: "فَٱحْذَرْهُمْ", l: "يَحْذَرُ", lc: 12, tl: "fa-iḥ'dharhum", lb: "ভয় করা",e: "so beware of them", b: "অতএব সতর্ক হও তাদের (থেকে)", i: "maka takutlah/waspadalah terhadap mereka", f: 1, rm: "To beware, take heed of, to be cautious/wary/vigilant, to take care, to be on ones guard, to be in a state of preparation, to fear or be in fear of, to be angry and prepare oneself to do mischief, draw oneself together, to be enraged.", ag: "فاء استئنافية وفعل أمر وضمير متصل ", eg: "Resumption fa and Verb Imperative and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPV", qual: "", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "حَٰذِرُونَ،يَحْذَرُ"},
